Name: WarpGate
Description: Enable Protoss to warp in units.

Root.Tooltip: Cancels construction of this structure, destroying the structure and giving a partial refund.
Root.Name: Cancel

Root.Tooltip:
A powerful melee warrior, as one of the few protoss elites, he can use Charge and Psionic Surge, and use the blue <Khala Psionic>to attack his enemies.

According to different levels of Khala Psionic, Dark Zealot gains the following different abilities:
Lv1 - Purifier Echo: Psionic Surge can regenerate extra shield in a few seconds
Lv2 - Dark Armor: This ability requires Zealot to be reforged as Dark Zealot.
Lv3 - Initiative: Dark Zealot will fight for a while in the battlefield after his died**Can attack ground**
Root.Name: Warp Zealot

Root.Tooltip:
A ranged unit in Sea of World, who used to be one of the most brave battlefield commanders of the protoss. She can use Psionic Projection and Psionic Teleport, and use the golden <Purification Psionic>Attack her enemies.

According to different levels of Purifier Psionic, Adept gains the following different abilities:
Lv1 - Resonating Glaives: Increase the attack speed of adept
Lv2 - Judgement Crit: Requires Adept to be reforged as War Adept.
Lv3 - Soul Elegy: Psionic Projection can store one more charge.**Can attack ground and air**
Root.Name: Warp Adept

Root.Tooltip: Deadly melee killer. Permanently invisible. Applying for the Nerazim tribe protocol can replace more threatening weapons and improve Blink ability.**Can attack the ground**
Root.Name: Warp In Dark Templar

Root.Tooltip: Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
Root.Name: Set Rally Point

Root.Tooltip: Transforms this Warp Gate back to a Gateway.
Root.Name: Transform to Gateway

Root.Tooltip:
Robotic support unit. Can use Shield Recharge and Guardian Shield.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp In Sentry

Root.Tooltip:
Purifier Faction
Ranged specialist. Can use Psionic Transfer.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp In Adept

Root.Tooltip:
Tal'darim Faction
Potent psionic master. Can use Psionic Orb, Mind Blast, and Sacrifice.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp In Ascendant

Root.Tooltip: Cancels construction of this structure, destroying the structure and giving a partial refund.
Root.Name: Cancel

Root.Tooltip: Powerful melee warrior. Has Charge and Whirlwind abilities.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Zealot

Root.Tooltip: Powerful melee warrior. Can be upgraded to use Charge and Reconstruction.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Sentinel

Root.Tooltip:
Short range warrior. Sacrifices itself to heal Alarak when he is near death. Supplicants are warped in two at a time.
**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp In Supplicant

Root.Tooltip: Powerful melee warrior. Has Shadow Charge and Darkcoil abilities.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Centurion

Root.Tooltip: Ranged support strider. Using Blink provides a shield restore.**Can attack ground and air units**
Root.Name: Warp in Stalker

Root.Tooltip: A long-range infantry mech with extra health and attack power. Applying for the Ara Tribe protocol allows Dragoon to attack extra targets and increase damage to air units.**Can attack the ground and air**
Root.Name: Warp In Dragoon

Root.Tooltip: This unit unlocks at Commander Level 8.
Root.Name: Warp In Ascendent

Root.Tooltip:
Nerazim Faction
Deadly warrior-assassin. Permanently cloaked. Can use Shadow Fury.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Dark Templar

Root.Tooltip:
Tal'darim Faction
Deadly warrior-assassin. Permanently cloaked. Can use Void Stasis.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Avenger

Root.Tooltip:
Aiur Faction
Robotic support unit. Can use Double Shield Recharge and Guardian Shield.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp in Sentry

Root.Tooltip:
Purifier Faction
Robotic support unit. Can use Protective Field and Phasing mode.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp in Conservator

Root.Tooltip:
Tal'darim Faction
Robotic support unit. Can use Target Lock, Squad Sight, and Force Field.
Root.Name: Warp In Havoc

Root.Tooltip:
Robotic support unit. Can use Chrono Beam and Phasing Mode. Can be upgraded to use Reclamation.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp in Energizer

Root.Tooltip: Mastery: Units warped in by this structure gain 0.0% attack speed.
Root.Name: Combat Mastery

Root.Tooltip: Powerful attack caster. Can Confuse and Mind Control enemies.**Can attack ground and air units**
Root.Name: Warp In Dark Archon

Root.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 5.
Root.Name: Warp In Dark Archon

Root.Tooltip:
Purifier Faction
Ranged support strider. Can store multiple Blink charges.**Can attack ground and air units**
Root.Name: Warp in Instigator

Root.Tooltip:
Aiur Faction
Deadly warrior-assassin. Permanently cloaked. Can use Recall on Death.**Can attack ground units**
Root.Name: Warp in Shadow Hunter

Root.Tooltip:
A deadly cloaked assassin in Sea of World, who used to be a powerful dark templar of Shakuras. He can use Shadow Asylum, Shadow Pace, and Dark Souls, and use the green <Void Psionic>Attack his enemies.

According to different levels of Void Psionic, Dark Templar gains the following different abilities:
Lv1 - Shadow Slaughter: Dark Templar deals additional damage to enemies with any debuff.
Lv2 - Soul Block: Requires Dark Templar to be reforged as Twilight Templar.
Lv3 - Intersection of Light and Shadow: Increase the shield of Dark Templar and strengthen Dark Souls.**Can attack the ground**
Root.Name: Warp Dark Templar

Root.Tooltip:
A psionic master, who used to be the most noble High Templar of the Protoss. He can use Psionic Feedback and Psi storm, and use white<Order Psionic>to attack his enemies.

According to different levels of Order Psionic, High Templars gain the following different abilities:
Lv1 - Mind Crystal: Increases the range of Psi storm.
Lv2 - Soul Block: This ability requires High Templar to be reforged as Light Archon.
Lv3 - Phase Shackles: High Templars will transfer to the phase and immune when they take fatal damage. **Can attack the ground and air**
Root.Name: Warp High Templar

Root.Tooltip: Karass' Gateway will automatically transform into Warpgate and can store infinite number of charges.
Root.Name: String of the Lost World
